The most efficient lawnmower is the reel lawnmower{{w|Lawn_mower#Reel (cylinder) mowers}} or cylinder lawnmower, which is powered by pushing. This also eliminates the [[noise pollution]] of conventional mowers. It is ideal for small to medium lawns, depending on your level of fitness. 

While a good choice of mower reduces energy use, other factors affect sustainability: see [[lawn care]].


